high_descs: Turn around, go forward to the counter, turn right, go forward to the counter, turn right, go forward, turn right at the kitchen island.
Take the apple from behind the lettuce on the kitchen island counter.
Turn right, go forward to the counter, turn left, go forward to the microwave.
Cook the apple in the microwave. Take the apple from the microwave.
Turn around, go forward to the counter, turn right, go forward, turn left at the trash bin after passing the fridge, go to the bin.
Put the apple in the bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked apple in a trash bin.

high_descs: Turn around to the other side of the kitchen island
Pick up the green apple from the top of the island
Put the apple inside the microwave, warm it for a second, and take the apple out
Turn around and go to the white bin
Place the apple into the bin
anns.task_desc: Place the warmed apple inside a bin

high_descs: Turn around, hang a right at the counter and walk to the back of the island counter on the right.
Pick up the green apple from the middle of the counter.
Turn right, hang a left and walk to the microwave.
Put the apple inside the microwave, heat it, remove it and close the door.
Turn around, take a right and walk to the gray bin on the floor to the left.
Put the heated apple inside the gray bin.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated apple in a bin.
